targets.query: SELECT percentile("duration", 95) FROM rails_transactions WHERE $timeFilter AND "action" = '[[action]]'
SELECT percentile("sql_duration", 95) FROM rails_transactions WHERE $timeFilter AND "action" = '[[action]]'
SELECT percentile("method_duration", 95) FROM rails_transactions WHERE $timeFilter AND "action" = '[[action]]'
SELECT percentile("cache_duration", 95) FROM rails_transactions WHERE $timeFilter AND "action" = '[[action]]'
SELECT percentile("duration", 95) AS "95th Percentile" FROM rails_method_calls WHERE $timeFilter AND "action" = '[[action]]' AND method =~ /^(Gitlab::Git|Rugged)/
SELECT percentile("view_duration", 95) FROM rails_transactions WHERE $timeFilter AND "action" = '[[action]]'
SELECT "duration_95th" AS "95th Percentile", "duration_mean" AS "Mean" FROM gitlab.downsampled.rails_transaction_timings_per_action WHERE $timeFilter AND "action" = '[[action]]'
SELECT "sql_duration_95th" AS "95th Percentile", "sql_duration_mean" AS "Mean" FROM gitlab.downsampled.rails_transaction_timings_per_action WHERE $timeFilter AND "action" = '[[action]]'
SELECT "view_duration_95th" AS "95th Percentile", "view_duration_mean" AS "Mean" FROM gitlab.downsampled.rails_transaction_timings_per_action WHERE $timeFilter AND "action" = '[[action]]'

SELECT "cache_duration_95th" AS "95th Percentile", "cache_duration_99th" AS "99th Percentile", "cache_duration_mean" AS "Mean" FROM gitlab.downsampled.rails_transaction_timings_per_action WHERE $timeFilter AND "action" = '[[action]]'

SELECT "duration_95th" AS "95th Percentile", "duration_99th" AS "99th Percentile", "duration_mean" AS "Mean" FROM gitlab.downsampled.rails_git_timings_per_action WHERE $timeFilter AND "action" = '[[action]]'
SELECT mean("duration_95th") AS "value" FROM gitlab.downsampled.rails_method_call_timings_per_action_and_method WHERE $timeFilter AND "action" = '[[action]]' GROUP BY "method", time($interval)

SELECT mean("duration_95th") AS "95th Percentile" FROM gitlab.downsampled.rails_view_timings_per_action_and_view WHERE $timeFilter AND "action" = '[[action]]' GROUP BY "view" ORDER BY time DESC LIMIT 100

SELECT "duration" AS "Duration", "allocated_memory" AS "Memory", "request_method" AS "Method", "action" AS "Action", "request_uri" AS "URI" FROM "rails_transactions" WHERE $timeFilter AND "action" ='[[action]]' ORDER BY time DESC LIMIT 100
